Summary: Gourmet Card Service for Employees of the Santa Cruz Palace Headquarters of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs, European Union and Cooperation. The Polytechnic University of Valencia has among its purposes training, research and the generation of knowledge, with the aim of promoting the comprehensive development of society and contributing to its technological, economic and cultural progress. It currently has three university campuses located in Valencia, Gandía and Alcoy, with around 40,000 daily users in its facilities, 120 buildings and more than 5,500 parking spaces available. The Institute of Molecular and Cellular Biology of Plants (IBMCP) is a university institute of joint research from the Polytechnic University of Valencia (UPV) and the Higher Council for Scientific Research (CSIC). To guarantee adequate safety conditions, both for people and property, it is necessary to have a surveillance and security service. Fundamentally these services consist of: • Protection of people and property • Surveillance and control of buildings and facilities • Surveillance and control of parking lots and outdoor areas • Connection of alarms buildings to Alarm Receiving Center and Acuda service in case of activation of the sensors. • Emergencies This contract is qualified as an administrative services contract in accordance with the provisions of articles 5, 12 and 17 of the LCSP. and will be governed, in terms of its preparation, adjudication, effects and termination, by this Law and, additionally, the remaining rules of applicable law will apply....
